{"tid":1564770,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"記者會—真相見解","createTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T01:52:15.000Z","uid":299104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"83a1d624efa9965b26f8a3fef44991d5abd224f4","tid":1564770,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:46:47.000Z","msg":"大家好，係度同大家討論關於記者會嘅幾點見解。<br />\n<br />\n1、記者會嘅本意：<br />\n記者會嘅本意就是<span style=\"color: red;\">民間了解/政府解釋事實</span>，不過好可惜嘅係依家記者會d講者，只不過係係度同d記者耍太極，用「我霖」、「通常來講」d虛無嘅字眼來繞過重點，所以下次記者會記得要專攻係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span></strong>度，知就知唔知就唔知，唔好比佢地再廢up。<br />\n<br />\n2、講者究竟知道幾多事實：<br />\n以正常公關角度來講，比得例d人出來講嘢肯定係經過篩選，除左揀好識辯駁嘅人，就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對事實一無所知嘅人</span></strong>。因為「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對事實一無所知嘅人先可以作出最真誠嘅否認</span></strong>」。消防署嘅記者會就係一個好好嘅例子。如果唔係就會好似popo咁出左個吃誠實豆沙包嘅 李桂華。自己收自己皮。"},{"pid":"e123c5a2602f79cc69183e9bc9fbe50ad90ba108","tid":1564770,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a9d1372c5f3929432626aa8cc15b43921faa0eef","tid":1564770,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a4b49475655ad8f6f8f